1:21:30.465 --> 1:21:33.368
I mean, he's dumb,
but he's not that dumb.

1:21:34.136 --> 1:21:36.469
Like, if he were okay he'd call.

1:21:36.471 --> 1:21:39.239
Maybe you should call him.

1:21:39.241 --> 1:21:41.343
Why? He's your husband.

1:21:41.811 --> 1:21:46.548
It would be such a human
gesture, a forgiving thing,

1:21:47.282 --> 1:21:54.656
considering the fact that even as
inadequate as he is, he loves you.

1:22:05.802 --> 1:22:07.870
Bet you've got him
to an accident.

